    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Process of creating mosaics using tiny pebbles set over three foundation layers: the bottom layer of large pebbles set on packed soil, second, of stone and gravel, crushed terracotta and Santorini powder from lava, and the top being a mixture of brick powder and fine sand that sets the pebbles.</Note_Text>
